You need a windows pkg installer: 

create a folder for vcpkg:

	ex: mkdir C:\dev\

Clone and build:
	git clone https://github.com/microsoft/vcpkg
	cd vcpkg
	bootstrap-vcpkg.bat

Install Curlpp:
	vcpkg install curlpp:x64-windows

Create bin for binaries:
	mkdir C:\dev\vcpkg\installed\x64-windows\bin

Build away!
